descriptionHtml:
Created a Dark Elf sin like character with mods and I think I should share her as she is rather easy on the eye. 

She is already level 9 now with some extras coins in her pocket so you will not have to worry about lacking anything. She is rich enough to buy all the houses and some more... :P

P.S: I killed Camilla Valerius and her brother while they were asleep... so don\'t think of marrying that one unless you roll back some saves....

P.S.S: If you don\'t like elves that look more human, this look may not be for you. I do, a lot. So I prefer my elves this way.


Mod used to get this effect:

Bright Eyes v1-3 by Skree000
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/2464

CBBE skin texture V2 V3 plus Thepal and UNP compatible by navetsea
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6554

HQ Eyebrows - vanilla texture replacers by Regn
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/21451

Human eyes for Elves (original) by PorcelynSkyrim
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/195

WSBP - Windsong Skyrim Beauty Project V1 by Windsong
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6066

ApachiiSkyHair by Apachii
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/10168
